04:01.452 --> 04:05.224
Portugal, sandwiched between
Spain and the Atlantic Ocean,

04:05.254 --> 04:06.985
and tiny as countries go,

04:07.025 --> 04:09.987
has had an outsized impact
on the world.

04:11.528 --> 04:13.390
During the Age of Discovery,

04:13.430 --> 04:15.961
the Portuguese went to sea
in great numbers,

04:15.991 --> 04:20.363
and gained fame as navigators,
ship builders, and explorers.

04:22.035 --> 04:23.937
They conquered
a large part of the world,

04:23.967 --> 04:26.268
their empire stretching
from Brazil,

04:26.298 --> 04:29.040
to Africa, to the East Indies.

04:32.773 --> 04:35.104
The city of Oporto
is a reflection

04:35.144 --> 04:39.607
and a creation of that
relationship with the sea.

04:39.647 --> 04:43.179
A lot has changed
since I was last here.

04:43.209 --> 04:44.250
Or has it?

05:04.294 --> 05:05.825
When I decided to return

05:05.865 --> 05:07.796
