first entre to Portugal.

05:12.499 --> 05:13.700
How you doing, man?

05:13.730 --> 05:15.371
- You look good.
- You good?

05:15.401 --> 05:17.833
- Yeah, nice to see you.
- It's been a long, long time.

05:17.873 --> 05:20.034
Jose is from the area
around Oporto,

05:20.074 --> 05:22.035
