07:15.151 --> 07:16.412
It would last a long time.

07:16.452 --> 07:17.712
And it usually is on Thursday.

07:17.753 --> 07:19.113
That's the day with the tripes,

07:19.153 --> 07:20.755
because being
a Catholic country,

07:20.785 --> 07:23.386
on Friday, they skip the meat.

07:26.258 --> 07:29.961
A meal here is, generally
speaking anyway, not light.

07:29.991 --> 07:31.922
The Portuguese like pork.

07:31.962 --> 07:33.793
They like it a lot.

07:33.823 --> 07:35.464
So sausage, bacon.

07:35.494 --> 07:38.096
- Sausage, pig's ear.
